{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-page-template-tsx","path":"/articles/gatsby-powered-vicblog-online","result":{"pageContext":{"id":"gatsby-powered-vicblog-online","lang":"cn","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么又换了？？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相信大家看到这个文章，第一反应如标题："},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么又换了？？"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上个寒假花了20天，用React+ASP.NET Core完整撸了一套博客网站出来。本以为就这样就可以了，结果却漏洞百出，且维护成本极高，例如："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"后端20请求能爆5个异常，大部分和网络请求有关（不知道为什么都在Azure上访问还是会很慢……"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没有管理员管理界面，甚至没有文章编辑器，写文章还得手动发POST请求，更别提图床（上传图片）了"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"性能很不好，每次访问界面都需要去Azure拿数据，放GitHub Pages上的前端虽然已经做了代码分割，可是在国内GitHub Pages的速度也是不敢恭维，导致每次访问博客的速度非常慢"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加功能成本极大，需要前后端都写。前后端分离有利于多人分工，可是却增大了工作量，对个人开发来说就是一种负担"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因此，这套完整的博客系统虽然功能强大和完整，但是日常维护起来可是非常难受。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby to the rescue!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","