xt","value":"为什么最后用Gatsby？"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高性能"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby最后生成的是静态网页，不需要折腾部署，并且便于被CDN和缓存"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"灵活，能够用上React和整个npm前端生态圈"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有人看到这个之前可能要问为什么不直接用hexo这种专门写博客的框架，这就是我的原因。hexo等这种静态博客工具过于局限，也不便于用上React等现在已经非常成熟的前端框架来让开发过程更加现代化。同样，Gatsby的灵活也便于扩展网站的功能和自定义。Gatsby有自己的生态系统，这个生态系统里的工具用起来有时还更爽更简单。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当然，Gatsby也是有坑的，例如一些开源项目通病"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文档不完整或者写得不好"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"网络上的教程质量不高"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第三方插件质量参差不齐"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只不过这些坑踩过之后影响不大，并且随着时间的推移越做越好了。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上线"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","val